從政老前輩教我的，我用了來玩狼人。<br />\n<br />\n玩人狼，我是村民，我沒有證據下懷疑誰是狼，我不會說出來，我只會投票時投。因為如果對方真的是狼，那對方就會先攻擊我，如果我猜錯了，我就變成破壞自己公信力。我是狼時，我就會隨便指控人，因為狼不會攻擊我，我的公信力下降也不是問題，煽動幾個較笨的村民一起指控，就可以混水摸魚。"},{"pid":"573c9d35b053343462c1020fdcd4306260f7c219","tid":258502,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:57:49.000Z","msg":"前幾日又話毓民回歸泛民，又話有五毛撐，而家扮無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3318ee22554270e490a374b6ad827ad043cdd985","tid":258502,"uid":54121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾成條怨婦咁 死左佢吧啦"},{"pid":"2ce2ad84d01ea026899d4cd796be867fd7ed51c4","tid":258502,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"返青山未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e21068c6b30c6483e5bc946ce16bb4bd06b879b","tid":258502,"uid":4389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢夠未呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢就係引毓民屌鳩佢<br />\n根本以前佢班教徒攻擊myradio佢係默許</blockquote><br />\n毓民真係要忍住唔好出聲屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪撚益佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ueeMeMokPgE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DueeMeMokPgE&d=ugRGr0K6dq0P6yXV8xHYtEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5405a078\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ueeMeMokPgE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請由11:55開始睇，好撚好笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃毓民寸鳩陳雲屈佢收美金，暗屌黃洋達同陳雲係撚人，名都費事提。"},{"pid":"a21e67958ef34c697e3468e8851bf3b4eaf7e18c","tid":258502,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:24:49.000Z","msg":"依家得番雲伯單機,熱血擺明唔理繼續做節目做議員,咪睇雲伯條友可以玩幾耐"},{"pid":"0b2d43c806b4b62fa17e91acc31c71cea7009aa3","tid":258502,"uid":